Class CommandBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.command.Command
      • org.mckenzierobotics.lib.robot.CommandBase
        • org.mckenzierobotics.y2012.commands.CommandBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.smartdashboard.SmartDashboardData, edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.smartdashboard.SmartDashboardNamedData
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CameraTrack, CheckCompressor, CoopertitionRamCommand, DriveCommand, EmptyCommand, RollerCommand, RollWithButtons, ShooterCommand, ShootWithOI, TeleopDrive, UpdateLCD

    public abstract class CommandBase
extends CommandBase
    The base for all commands, also the class defining robot hardware/config. All atomic commands should subclass CommandBase. CommandBase stores creates and stores each control system.
    Author:
    Luke Shumaker
